        "Minor in Theatre": [
            "Minor in Theatre The Minor in Theatre provides students practical and scholarly courses in Theatrical Arts. Students interested in declaring a Minor in Theatre must take and pass the Rowan general education course, Experiencing Acting, and obtain a letter of approval from the instructor. The Minor in Theatre Arts consists of 19 semester hours of study: 10 semester hours of required courses, plus 9 hours of electives."
        ],
